Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巡航导弹 好像全都被对方给拦截了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饱和攻击好像不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔纳奇斯伯爵的重甲骑兵——灼热的索利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.47,ruby,NTP,665,0,0,,Solis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其搭载的光束武器的射程甚至可以打到卫星基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而无法进行高空支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不得了的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强袭部队来电
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们即将上陆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射巡航导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吸引对方的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来就只有突入敌阵这一条路可走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全驾驶员开始搭乘机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 出击准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韵子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韵子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 莱埃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是紧急搜查那谁的下落吗…叫马…马…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马兹卢卡伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是怎样跑掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆会知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样问？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是去审讯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没从他口中听到什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 韵子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到用这么一个小小的装置就可以指示方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是在只有磁场的星球上才会有的装置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 托罗亚特伯爵和界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位都是地球出身的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为单纯所以才不会迷茫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话真是真理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的要去决斗吗 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 既然接到挑战我就不能退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我允许马丽尔晌伯爵的来访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这都多亏了雷姆蕾娜公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是展示我力量的绝佳机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我赢了这场决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以以此来牵制那些不满我的轨道骑士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您完全不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 你可能真的会实现自己的梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有什么梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾被蔑视的地球人掌握了巴斯的实权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们第一次见面的时候我就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我之间有什么地方很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算永不忘记对皇族的怨恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与巴斯血统毫无瓜葛的你不断赢得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是赏心乐事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一直无法忘怀吧…皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很爱她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…你愿意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我也助你一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算当皇姐的替代品…也无所谓…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各小队 向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Belgian小队 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maremmano小队 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pottok小队 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lokai小队 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang小队 配置完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的光束攻击无法躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被发现了就认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以干扰红外线及雷达波的烟幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clydesdale队长呼叫小队各机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向南部散开并张开烟幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火 开火 开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续将对方的注意力吸引到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要被击中了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一边吸引火力 还得不被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要怎么做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放你上去 请小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱埃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 我来中转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声学分析 敌人坐标定位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标位于 29951103 -90085579
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 瞄准目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒计时5 4 3 2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着弹 修正037 025
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从海那边打来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰炮射击吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.82,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Unknown soldier lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.78,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Explosions forever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.45,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now you take me away from danger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光学武器只能直线攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:09.50,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We had always covered up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要藏在地球的曲线背后 对方就无法打中我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.67,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Out there who will watch your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们的炮弹会因为地球的引力而做抛物线运动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.55,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Because I don't know if I can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们可以打到水平线的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.63,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.84,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Now we hate our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能瞄准就可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修正283 -472
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:24.77,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}No longer can move my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超高速炮弹发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.52,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.23,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.69,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.23,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！连观测卫星都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.48,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎样获得正确坐标的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.19,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:42.49,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.12,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来转播激光通信的无人机被击毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.99,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法和界冢少尉取得联络
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱埃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射拽光弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据我的指示发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.60,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.31,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拽光弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.77,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得可以从那个距离打败我的索利斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.31,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.56,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪姐 快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.27,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢准尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:20.57,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2发…接着是3发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.20,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修正002 003 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.07,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.91,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And I remember a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.54,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在那里嚣张地呆站着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.91,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在灼热的光辉下化为灰烬吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.46,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Better you believe your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本身你就开炮啊！你这青蛙脑袋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过被打掉了一只胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 界冢少尉也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明叫你赶紧跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是违反命令 界冢准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 别比我高一个等级就装老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我本来就是你的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上不存在可以命令姐姐的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clydesdale队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战结束 返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是盛开在地球上的名为玫瑰的花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决斗真的没问题吗 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以命相搏的战斗 迄今我已经经历很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在担心我吗 艾德尔丽泽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前经常瞪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那都是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玫瑰有许多不同的花语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红玫瑰代表着“我爱你”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝玫瑰的意思是“奇迹”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是蓝玫瑰还有着另一个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也许就是真实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Herschel 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您武运昌隆 斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人的傲慢举动实在滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上巴斯轨道骑士的名誉 由我来处决你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于私利而篡夺官职的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止会打乱秩序 更会扰乱社会的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为公主的卫士 我来教你做人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在将举行马丽尔晌伯爵和托罗亚特伯爵的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟传闻说的一样 跑得比谁都快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你逃得出这架Herschel的攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算可以预测 也没办法应对如此多的数量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 你还会动一下脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徒劳的！徒劳的！全都是徒劳的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝玫瑰的花语为“奇迹”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个意义是…“不可能实现的事”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的已经不会再醒来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请降临奇迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹是不会发生的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只会跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这劣等民族！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆？你在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经无处可逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无处可逃的人可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Herschel特长是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从各个方向进行同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在这里 攻击被限制到了一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是月球基地建设时所使用的物资搬运通道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找这里好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能打倒我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我 地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托罗亚特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照规定 马丽尔晌伯爵的所有资产
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将被转让给斯雷因·扎赫巴姆·托罗亚特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我巴鲁库如斯伯爵作为见证人…认可这个结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是什么都能看见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却看不到自己真正想要知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韵子 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想把你给卷进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向37氏族的诸位传达我们即将通过的新政策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经在地球上获得了资源和土地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此不再需要一直依靠巴斯母星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子终将成人 离开父母的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将下嫁斯雷因·扎赫巴姆·托罗亚特伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球圈上建立新的王国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.07,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“穿越深邃之林”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:41.97,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕たちは彷徨える未来　窮屈な空に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:41.97,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在彷徨的未来 在狭隘的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:46.30,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ヒカリを探している
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:46.30,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我们探寻光明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.35,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}震える手は無力で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.35,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}颤抖着的双手是无力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.73,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}叫びはまだ遠くて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.73,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}呐喊又尚在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:21:02.15,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}だけど飛ぶことを　恐れではいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:21:02.15,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}然而对于飞翔 绝不能感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:10.16,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}永遠じゃなくても　完璧じゃなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:10.16,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不永恒又何妨 不完美又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:17.58,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}背中合わせの世界を真っ直ぐ生きてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:17.58,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要在相互扶持的世界勇敢生存
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:24.76,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何度傷ついても　何度間違えても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:24.76,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一次次的受伤算什么 一次次的错误算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:30.43,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}運命さえ飛び超えていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:30.43,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使是命运 我们也要一起飞越
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:34.06,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この宙の果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:34.06,EDJP2,NTP,0,95,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\fs17}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:34.06,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}飞向宇宙的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:40.15,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}創造を信じで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:40.15,EDJP2,NTP,0,130,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\fs17}はじまり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:40.15,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}相信着希望的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言 皇姐你是我憧憬的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既美丽又善良 更为人们所爱戴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有我所没有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一样东西是我们都拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是皇家的血脉 Aldnoah的启动因子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于现今的斯雷因而言是必要的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我选择了斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因也选择了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后 我就是亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是皇姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你已经不用再坚持了 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是个人偶 你也依然是我的皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你做一个好梦

